import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import styled from 'styled-components'

export default function Navigation (){
    return (<>
        <Nav class="navi">
            <NavList>
                <NavItem><Link to='/add'>add</Link></NavItem>
                <NavItem><Link to='/detail'>detail</Link></NavItem>
                <NavItem><Link to='/list'>list</Link></NavItem>
                <NavItem><Link to='/login'>login</Link></NavItem>
                <NavItem><Link to='/modify'>modify</Link></NavItem>
                <NavItem><Link to='/remove'>remove</Link></NavItem>
            </NavList>
        </Nav>
</>)
}
